    "description": "Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates is actively seeking a talented and motivated Reservation Manager to join our dynamic team in Patna. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates:\nMenzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates!",
